      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BRAVADO (5) drew the inside and won last time at Healesville over 300m (16.58) after forging to the front and leading throughout, scoring by 1.5 lengths. The one to beat again. HYLAND AZULA (8) could not have been more impressive a few runs back in her solid 23.96 win at Bendigo over 425m then has finished in the placings in both runs since. Should be in this for a long way. ORIENTAL OPHELIA (1) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by a neck at this track in a handy 22.39 beating Don't Tell Danni. Expected to feature again. DIM SIM OLLIE (3) comes off a big run when finishing third in a quick 19.40 last time. Has claims on that run.",
